  "title": "Facility Technician",
  "description": "<p><u>Responsibilities</u></p><p>To maintain/upgrade the plant mechanical equipmentalongside with team of production colleagues and technicians</p><p>·       Supports, lead troubleshooting andrectification of plant equipment as assigned </p><p>·       Carry out routine checks and testingof plant equipment based on job requests as per good maintenance practice</p><p>·       Ensure safety and housekeeping are alwaysobserved </p><p>·       Support production departments onContinuous Improvement, Preventive Maintenance to ensure high levels of lineefficiency and line performance<br /></p><p><u><strong>Skillsets/Qualifications Needed</strong></u></p><p>·      \nNITEC/Higher\nNITEC/Diploma in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent</p><p>·Strong technical knowledge and hands on skills in a manufacturing environment for Facility\nrelated equipment like chiller, compressor, Air handling unit, boiler, etc.</p><p>o   Able to perform metal fabrication and\nable to use mechanical tools like welding machine, drill press, etc.</p><p>o   Able to read and understand\nmechanical drawings and able to understand drawing specifications.</p><p>o   Strong knowledge in plant facility\nequipment and good troubleshooting skills.</p><p>o   Able to conduct training to\ntechnicians and operators.</p><p>Must be willing to rotate on 12 hrs shift from 730 to 730<a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
